      <t>This document defines the Segment Routing IPv6 Prefix-SID in the IPv4/IPv6 Extended Reachability Attribute Flags TLV. The new flag is used for advertising the capability to handle the IPv6 Segment Routing header for the prefix that has the flag attached.</t>
